comments.body:
@worldofgeese Podman officially supports windows arm64 since release v5.5.0. My guess is that you are downloading the old x64 installer (podman-5.7.1-setup.exe) and that explains why machine init is failing. 

You should uninstall your current version of Podman and run the new arm64 installer ([podman-installer-windows-arm64.msi](https://github.com/containers/podman/releases/download/v5.7.1/podman-installer-windows-arm64.msi)).

Please confirm if that solves your problem.
